InsertDateTimeTypes: INSERT INTO DATETIME_TEST (F_ID, F_DATE, F_DATE_NULLABLE, F_TIME, F_TIMESTAMP, F_TIMESTAMP_NULLABLE, F_NAME) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
SelectDateTimeById: SELECT F_DATE, F_DATE_NULLABLE, F_TIME, F_TIMESTAMP, F_TIMESTAMP_NULLABLE, F_NAME FROM DATETIME_TEST WHERE F_ID = ?
SelectAllDateTime: SELECT F_ID, F_DATE, F_DATE_NULLABLE, F_TIME, F_TIMESTAMP, F_TIMESTAMP_NULLABLE, F_NAME FROM DATETIME_TEST
UpdateTimestamp: UPDATE DATETIME_TEST SET F_TIMESTAMP = ? WHERE F_ID = ?
SelectDateGreater: SELECT F_DATE, F_NAME FROM DATETIME_TEST WHERE F_DATE > ?
